{"tid":782791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男人大忌頭髮出事？連加特不滿《FIFA 19》沒有更新其髮型","createTime":"2018-08-17T04:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T09:57:31.000Z","uid":161311,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf21e6602c6e7e97510301919b94d771ba1585e","tid":782791,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"電玩遊戲《FIFA》每一集都吸引大量玩家，特別是球員的模樣與現實非常相似，因此受到外界讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n不過，曼聯球星連格及水晶宮前鋒韋費特沙夏卻有不滿，因為他們的髮型近年都是一模一樣，彷彿完全沒有更新過一樣。<br />\n<br />\n因為不滿EA Sports沒有更新其髮型，連格直接在Twitter上詢問此事，甚至寫了一句：「你們可以更新我的頭髮嗎？因為我在遊戲中的髮型已經用了99年。」<br />\n<br />\n看看連格在《FIFA 18》遊戲中的髮型與世界盃決賽周期間的髮型，確實是有點不同。除了連格，韋費特沙夏也是受害人，看看他在新季英超上陣時的頭髮，和遊戲中的頭髮也不一樣。沙夏的頭髮轉變比起連格明顯，他也嘗試直接向EA Sports查問，結果對方尚未回應，Konami的《Pro Evolution Soccer》已經出手，表示他們已經幫沙夏改了髮型云云。兩大電玩公司暗中過招，到底EA Sports又會如何回應？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/125333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F125333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0564ba45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcff8ddba395549ddf6eff00540434212469ab59","tid":782791,"uid":58811,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"髮型點改都咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c02f1d8a507c6c5712424e159fd8ad650d6b53","tid":782791,"uid":73422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"嗰時沙拿同古天奴個頭都要等咗幾集先有更新啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520fc3b83ec9fb767d333979e73f4a29961ecfd2","tid":782791,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"特別是球員的模樣與現實非常相似，因此受到外界讚賞。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d676fd82831d4b8f6a931f870f1d25bc60bcc76e","tid":782791,"uid":34508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"諗起Khedira<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a762c6709e061924481d2612fd6a39388c56d13","tid":782791,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5abf6798d8e99e721086838eea4fa0bab22f1f10","tid":782791,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a762c6709e061924481d2612fd6a39388c56d13","tid":782791,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcff8ddba395549ddf6eff00540434212469ab59","tid":782791,"uid":58811,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"髮型點改都咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9061a1cc23c58f3c47217a6c1b82599fafc154a5","tid":782791,"uid":37050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢條友係真心覺得自己好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c013e1d28b8dd43a8a94daad56e73ee71d30722","tid":782791,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9061a1cc23c58f3c47217a6c1b82599fafc154a5","tid":782791,"uid":37050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢條友係真心覺得自己好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889bfb